    public class ExpressionComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<SymbolicExpression>
    Comparator of symbolic expressions. Creation order: first create ObjectComparator oc. Then create NumericComparator nc using oc. Then create ExpressionComparator ec using oc and nc.
